latestIgtvVideos.title: My strength! My idol! 100k is dedicated to my brother, my guru @bijendra_s
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Who is Pawan Chechi!? 

This name was lost as any other names in the translation in life until the day I met my idol, guru, brother, mentor. He was everything to me! He helped me gain the clarity in life and thought me many lessons on where to divert your mind. Staying positive and focused! Whatever that I am today is only because of this MAN! It’s unfortunate that he is not here with us physically however mentally you are always forever with me! 

My Instagram account was created and managed by him, as I had no idea of social media and how it worked, but with a little drive and determination from my brother. I was able to make the name PAWAN CHECHI! And I owe this 100k to him and my lovely followers! Thank you I wouldn’t have done this with your love and support!!! 🙏🏽❤️

I also want to take this moment to end this 2020 by thanking my entire team, who have always stood next to me in happiness and sadness, I will forever be thankful for everything I have received from my friends! Thank you and I love u all from the bottom of my heart! ❤️ 

A message for my brother @bijendra_s 

An eternal memory....
.... UNTIL WE MEET AGAIN....
Those special memories of you will always bring a smile
If only I could have you back for just a little while, Then we could sit and talk again just like we use to do.  You always meant so very much and always will do too! The fact that you’re no longer here will always cause a pain BUT you’re forever in my heart UNTIL WE MEET AGAIN!
Love you and miss you always and forever! ❤️🙏🏽
